    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously gotta see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine, showroom condition\u2014I\u2019ve honestly babied it since the day I brought it home. It\u2019s been garage-kept, meticulously detailed, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels and looks brand new, this is definitely the one for you! I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions, I'm happy to chat!",
      "price": 46500.0,
