    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute showroom-quality masterpiece that defies the 'used' label. This vehicle has been meticulously pampered in a climate-controlled garage and shows zero signs of wear. The exterior paint retains its original factory luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating that ensures a deep, mirror-like finish with no swirl marks, chips, or scratches. Step inside to find a cabin that still carries the distinct scent of fresh premium leather; the seats are pristine with no bolster compression or creasing, and the high-gloss interior trim is entirely free of micro-scratches. Every technological feature, from the intuitive heads-up display to the adaptive cruise control, operates with precision. Mechanically, this car is flawless, backed by a comprehensive, paper-documented service history performed exclusively by certified master technicians. It features brand-new Michelin Pilot Sport tires and has never seen a day of inclement weather. For the discerning buyer who demands perfection, this is the finest example currently available on the market.",
      "price": 46500.0,
